        <h3 class="font-extralight text-2xl md:text-5xl text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-500 leading-relaxed overflow-hidden whitespace-nowrap border-r-4 border-black animate-typing w-fit">
          Ingeniero Civil en Informática
        </h3>
      </div>
